Motormaster looks at the new robot, then hears the voice in his head. "Okay
rookie, your up," he points towards Condor, "hit him, and your in the
group, just dont kill him". Motormaster takes off of the ground, and starts
to fly towards Condor, letting his Cyclone cannon blast once towards Condor.
